# Installation of GHC 8.2.2

## Installation Script

~~~
# get distribution   
cd $HOME/Downloads  
wget https://downloads.haskell.org/~ghc/8.2.2/ghc-8.2.2-x86_64-deb8-linux.tar.xz

tar xvfJ ghc-8.2.2-x86_64-deb8-linux.tar.xz

cd ghc-8.2.2 

# install  
mkdir $HOME/Software/ghc-8.2.2  

./configure --prefix=$HOME/Software/ghc-8.2.2  
make install

# cleanup: remove temporary files  
cd ..  
rm -rfv ghc-8.2.2*
~~~

## Activation Script

~~~
switchghc 8.2.2 
~~~